\c 1
\s Isiraeri naJudha vachaparadzwa nokuda kwezvivi zvavo
\p
\v 1 "Shoko raJehovha, rakauya kuna Mika weMoresheti namazuva aJotamu naAhazi naHezekia, madzimambo aJudha, raakaona pamusoro peSamaria neJerusaremu.
\p
\v 2 "Inzwai imi marudzi avanhu, imi mose; teerera iwe nyika, nezvose zvirimo; Ishe Jehovha ngaakupupurirei, iye Ishe ari mutemberi yake tsvene.
\v 3 Nokuti tarirai, Jehovha anobuda panzvimbo yake, achaburuka nokutsika panzvimbo dzakakwirira dzenyika.
\v 4 Makomo achanyauka pasi pake, mipata ichapamuka senamo yakaiswa pamoto, semvura inodururwa pamawere.
\p
\v 5 "Zvose izvi zvinoitwa nokuda kwokudarika kwaJakobho, uye nokuda kwezvivi zveimba yaIsiraeri. Kudarika kwaJakobho ndokweiko? Harizi Samaria here? Nzvimbo dzakakwirira dzaJudha ndedzipiko? Harizi Jerusaremu here?
\v 6 Saka Samaria ndichariita somurwi wamabwe musango, senzvimbo dzingasimwa mizambiringa; ndichakandira mabwe aro mumupata, ndichifukunura nheyo dzaro.
\v 7 Mifananidzo yaro yose yakavezwa ichaputswa-putswa, mibairo yaro yose ichapiswa nomoto, uye ndichaparadza zvifananidzo zvaro zvose; nokuti rakazviunganidza izvo uri mubayiro wechifeve, naizvozvi zvichadzokerazve kumubayiro wechifeve.
\p
\v 8 "Nemhaka iyi ndichachema nokuungudza, ndichafamba ndisina nguo ndakashama, ndichaungudza samakava nokurira semhou.
\v 9 Nokuti mavanga aro haadi kupora, nokuti zvasvika kuna Judhawo; zvisvikira pasuo ravanhu vangu, ipo paJerusaremu.
\p
\v 10 "Musazvireva paGati, regai kutongochema; paBheti-re-Afura ndakaumburuka muguruva.
\v 11 Chibva uende, iwe ugere Shafiri, wakashama uchinyara; agere Zaanani haana kubuda kuungudza paBheti-ezeri kuchakutorera pokumira.
\v 12 Nokuti agere Maroti anomirira zvikuru chinhu chakanaka, nokuti zvakaipa zvakaburuka zvichibva kuna Jehovha zvikasvikira kusuo reJerusaremu.
\v 13 Iwe ugere Rakishi, sunga mabhiza pangoro; ndiro rakatanga kuisa mukunda weZiyoni pazvivi, nokuti kudarika kwalsiraeri kwakawanikwa mauri.
\v 14 Saka iwe uchapa Moresheti-gati chipo chokuonekana; dzimba dzeAkizibhi dzichava chinhu chinonyengera madzimambo aIsiraeri.
\p
\v 15 "Iwe ugere Maresha, ndichakuuyisira mumwe achakukunda; vakakudzwa valsiraeri vachasvika paAdhurami.
\v 16 Zviitire mhazha, vevura vhudzi rako pamusoro pavana vaunofarira; kurisa mhazha yako seyegondo, nokuti vakatapwa kure newe.
